Author: suckmydickbitxh
Text: Be careful with marking tw for self harm as it greatly effects me. But I’ll move on from that. You’re not a clown, I hope however you do choose to see someone or keep venting here. Expression is really needed, especially in moments you feel out of control. If you ever need an actual human to talk to in crisis, there is always me and this entire community. I bet anything you can PM anyone in this group and it would be welcomed.  Be safe please.
